require 'date'
<h1>Eldest director</h1>

<p>The eldest director in our dataset right now is 
<%director_list = Director.where.not({ :dob => nil }).order({ :dob => :asc })%>
<%oldest = director_list.at(0)%>
<a href="/directors/<%=oldest.id%>"><%=oldest.name%></a>, born on <%=oldest.dob.strftime('%B %d, %Y')%> .</p>

<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>
